data.description: Welcome home to this wonderful, traditional two story in the heart of Farmington. A newly renovated kitchen and recently finished basement are both stunning additions to this well cared for gem, maintaining all the character and charm you could ever want, with original hardwoods and coved ceilings inside to the beautiful brick front and paver driveway as you arrive. Four bedrooms on one level, a huge screened porch, peaceful yard out back and an oversized garage make this the one! **BRAND NEW roof and kitchen, come see it today**
